Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Intruder alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you have found\NPascalle's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That virus program hidden in her mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,was the only thing that\Never threatened me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we have her, nothing can stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I command you to kill her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you\Ncan make me kill Lilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you defy me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not defiance, just the truth.\NI can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,do not be deceived by your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I loaded it to your brain\Nfrom the real Rion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a Galerian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to your Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm not the real Rion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you did create me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilia... ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!\NThere's no need to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my greatest failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have created you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should have raised you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I command you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Death shall be your only salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorothy, please stop!
